      },
      "rationale": "Construct stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement are the three QoIs specified in ASTM F1717 and referenced in FDA guidance on spinal system submissions (FDA 2017 guidance on testing of spinal implants). Yield force directly relates to the clinical failure mode of screw-rod construct plastic deformation leading to loss of fixation. Linkage documented in Simulation Plan SP-2021-03 Section 3.2."
